I"<h1 id="openproject-422">OpenProject 4.2.2</h1>

<p>OpenProject 4.2.2 contains additional translations for the OpenProject
core and plugins, for instance complete translations for French
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20798">#20798</a>).</p>

<p>Additionally, some bugs have been fixed:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Several wrong English translations have been fixed – in the core and
in plugins
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20901">#20901</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20902">#20902</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20859">#20859</a>).</li>
  <li>The last login is no longer visible in the user profile
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20892">#20892</a>).</li>
</ul>

<p>For further information on the release, please refer to the <a href="https://community.openproject.org/versions/729">Changelog
v.4.2.2</a> or take a look
at <a href="https://github.com/opf/openproject/tree/v4.2.2">GitHub</a>.</p>

